          <h2 class="featurette-heading">Presentations<span class="text-muted">&nbsp;that inspire and motivate people</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">Mind maps are great for brainstorming and planning, but not that good for presenting. A great story
          has a beginning and an end, a sequence of thoughts, suspense and  carefully planned discovery of information.</p>
          <p class="lead">MindMup helps professional
          presenters bring their ideas to the audience better by bridging that gap. Use a frictionless planning canvas to capture and 
          organise your thoughts, and then put them into a powerful storyboard to turn a hierarchy of ideas into a sequence of slides.</p>
          <p><%=erb :version_buttons%></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
