          <p>Export your storyboard to Powerpoint format with one click. Import that into your preferred presentation software to fine tune slide design, animate transitions, integrate into conference templates or add 
          anything that MindMup does not yet support. </p>
          <a class="btn btn-default" href="/storyboards#exporting" role="button">More info »</a>
        </div>
